description: Bonäsudden Holding AB engages in the provision of real estate services. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 0 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2015-07-03. The firm operates as the parent company of Bonasudden Fastighets AB, a real estate company managed by Pareto Business Management AB and Fastighetspartner P&E AB. The firm's portfolio includes approximately 36,000 square meters, spread across 20 buildings in the greater Linkoping area. The firm's rental properties include public tenants, such as municipalities and county councils, among others. In addition, the Company has rental apartments, offices, shops, storage rooms and parking lots, among others. The firm operates domestically, on the territory of Sweden.
